1 HOT WRAP INSTOCK! :D


Marie France "REBORN" Slimming Wrap
Really Very effective! tried & tested by many in last sprees!
Many spree-ers commented they lost INCHES just after 1-2 USE!


Description: Comes in 2 kinds - Hot & Cold. Very easy to use at your own time and own place :) use the slimming wrap for 30 - 45 mins and you can see results!
For areas that are fatter, use the hot wrap for better effects.
For areas that are flabby, use the Cold Wrap.




Looks like this. One roll can use 2 to 3 times.


(Hot) :-Reduces fat & reduces swolleness-Stimulates the cells & increases metabolism. Helps to get rid of excess water that is retained in our body. Increases body ability to break down sugar, decreases the chance of carbohydrates turning into fats

(Cold): Reduces fat & tightens skin-Strengthens the skin's elasticity and tightens skin so as to reduce fine lines. Prevents cellulite & helps to eliminate toxins in our body.

Ingredients: Made with natural plant extracts including Paullinia, Cupana, Hedera Helix extract, Ginger extract essence, Chilli pepper oil, etc. No alcohol, won't cause skin sensitivity; no side effects. Also added are moisturising ingredients so the skin is protected all round & gives a gleaming effect after use.

before treatment



Wrap it in sling wrap



redness due to blood circulation


Gone down by 1 cm!


 1.Best to use after your shower. Otherwise, use a warm wet cloth to clean the area you want to put the wrap on before using the slim wrap.
2. Wrap the slim wrap round the area you want to use on as many times as you like.
3. Use the plastic cling wrap to hold the slim wrap in place.
4. Use scotch tape to hold all the wraps together.
5. Bind for 30 to 45 minutes.
6. After use, massage the surplus essence into your skin until its absorbed.
7. Use a warm towel to wipe the wrapped area (optional)
Note: For those who are using massaging cream already, you can use the slim wrap after using the massaging cream. It is normal to feel a heating sensation as the slimming wrap helps in blood circulation. If too hot for you to bear, just put it into the fridge and take it out when you want to try again.




Product Specifications:
1. Each wrap can be used for 2 to 3 times.
2. Measures about 2.5m * 15cm
3. Use once every 2 - 3 days. Usage of 15 times is considered as 1 treatment course.
4. Recommended usage: 1 cold wrap after every 2-4 hot wraps.
5. Every treatment course is said to be able to help you to lose 5 to 10 kg. :)

Storage Method:
1. Place in original bag after use & store in the fridge to maintain freshness.
2. If don't want to place in fridge, just store in a cool and dry place.

Do not wrap too tightly or add other creams that you have for better results.
Do not apply on wounds or broken skin :)

Some common questions

Q: Can we use normal cleansing solution like complete to wash, soak?

Q: When will lenses arrive?

Q: Do you provide astig lenses? Can we order diff degrees for both sides?
A: yes, astig lenses can be made for bescon lens. and yes, you can order diff degrees for both sides.

Q: What is your cleansing regime like?
